{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Flyknight</strong> tells the tale of a squire of the order of the Flyknights who is assembled to vanquish the witch <strong>Lunamoth</strong> and lift her curse, which is preventing the denizens of the realm from growing wings. Now separated after an ambush, the squire arriveth at the village of the swamp folk and pledges to see the mission through, either alone or teaming up with other fighters summoned to help along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to emerge victorious and claim Knighthood?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/BannerGif01.gif?t=1738488974\" />Arm yourself with an arsenal of weapons and choose what's best for the situation at hand: chop off a foe's arm to prevent aggression, crush their head to deprive them of senses, fight out of their range with long weapons or arrows. Approach each encounter tactically to prevail! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/BannerGif05.gif?t=1738488974\" />Traverse a <strong>hand crafted</strong> environment with many sidepaths filled with loot and dangerous encounters, survive from checkpoint to checkpoint and prove your skills against fierce bosses that want you dead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/BannerGif02.gif?t=1738488974\" />Summon a friend and progress through Lunamoth's lair together: divide and conquer, trade items and make gestures. 2 to 4 players can play together and progress is saved for everyone involved!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/BannerGif03-small.gif?t=1738488974\" />Take a breather at checkpoints and pull out your fishing rod. Fill up your fish bag with nutritious creatures that will give you buffs and advantages in combat should you use them wisely...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/BannerGif04.gif?t=1738488974\" />Thorough exploration of the dungeon will yield great rewards, customize your equipment to your hearts content and build a character that feels your own.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Lotus Flyeater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3108510/44ebb994623087615ba9a39a312bf74e5d6a0715.jpg"},{"name":"Dragoonflychild","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3108510/e613735c62ce085d976e79cb6839325fa8d61bac.jpg"},{"name":"Pretty sly for a Fly Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3108510/4ea40ff0eb949be73153d0b1782b335658ceeb20.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing For Fishies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3108510/ae6f232beaffd792b66af8c91884a9eb30e115e1.jpg"},{"name":"F.L.Y.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3108510/e204b695f831f68b239f78e0116cba32d919cddd.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738488974","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738488974","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/71232cfb1c006490347921424120bc82ee32d0d0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738488974","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/71